    "description": "<p>Incisive Law LLC is an independent Singapore Law Practice qualified to provide expert advice on Singapore law and other laws including English law. We offer a full spectrum of legal services to local and multinational corporations across various sectors. We routinely representat clients in matters before the Singapore Courts, in domestic and international arbitrations, and in major projects in Southeast Asia and beyond. In addition to being advocates with rights of audience before the Singapore Courts and Tribunals, Incisive Law also provides notarial services.</p>",
